The course introduces the geography subject in school, its purposes and expected outcomes and the most important topics in geography. The course also introduces geography teacher daily work and career possibilities when becoming a science teacher. The course focuses on developing learners self-analysis, reflection and learning competence.Objectives/eesmärkid:  1) To give an overview about teaching geography at school. 2) To increase an awareness about science teacher profession. 3) To support learners self-analysis, reflection and learning competence for career awareness.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  1) Understands the purpose and excepted outcomes in geography as school subject. 2) Has an overview of the most important topics in geography as school subject. 3) Has an awareness about science teacher career opportunities. 4) Has obtained self-analysis, reflection and learning competence.
